    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep gloss and zero imperfections, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather upholstery still firm and smelling new, and all electronic components functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and very low mileage. A buyer can expect a vehicle that looks and drives like it has never been used.",
