      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's in incredible shape, super clean inside and out, and drives like a total dream. If you're looking for something that's been loved and pampered, this is the one. Come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you'll fall in love!",
      "price": 44900.0,
